扎醒咗 起身果下極度空虛＋失落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2034e9251ef60f7f9bbc1a23ecc2436132cbd4d","tid":849484,"uid":207161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T23:16:02.000Z","msg":"我周不時都會，感覺好真實<br />\n但係一醒返就好空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d44c7f21a2756ebce2d1bbb186e1c9801a1de4a","tid":849484,"uid":15669,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T23:18:43.000Z","msg":"分左手3年 仲係會夢到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到而家都仲未有下一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd13f9c6adb7c4efc8f39ebe70c8cd4316c4e914","tid":849484,"uid":203918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:32:27.000Z","msg":"夢入面可以見佢真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb76e5b4157f7aa3c2ad6f4961bc93634cef3e8","tid":849484,"uid":52406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd13f9c6adb7c4efc8f39ebe70c8cd4316c4e914","tid":849484,"uid":203918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:32:27.000Z","msg":"夢入面可以見佢真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:37:11.000Z","msg":"醒嗰下真係想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959a829c0add194fa184cb1f88b6bf4db514f180","tid":849484,"uid":203918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bb76e5b4157f7aa3c2ad6f4961bc93634cef3e8","tid":849484,"uid":52406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd13f9c6adb7c4efc8f39ebe70c8cd4316c4e914","tid":849484,"uid":203918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:32:27.000Z","msg":"夢入面可以見佢真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:37:11.000Z","msg":"醒嗰下真係想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:41:09.000Z","msg":"本身無佢嘅生活都想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯一真心開心嘅途徑就係喺夢入面同佢講想講嘅嘢<br />\n但最近一次夢到佢有男友了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c463da4ed1f3ab0945247c3676bdd9ef0d7ec94","tid":849484,"uid":43342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:48:33.000Z","msg":"有，被分左差唔多一個月。頭兩個星期發夢同佢繼續sweet住拍拖，或者見佢搵返我。最近嘅星期發夢見到自己用唔同方法想佢回心轉意，但係夢入面嘅佢都係拒絕左。<br />\n<br />\n可能係潛意識嘅轉變，剛剛開始覺得有得挽回，而家慢慢明白，就算點挽回佢都唔會返黎。就算發夢見到佢挽留我，自己會喺個夢入面發現自己發緊夢，因為深深明白到佢係唔會咁做，一切都只係幻想。"},{"pid":"ce92b8f459e9b87809046a38bce43edf7c3c96fc","tid":849484,"uid":79632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:49:06.000Z","msg":"啱啱又夢見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 瞓唔返"},{"pid":"bd65a6db3441630616ef3d5d032090557b018483","tid":849484,"uid":58528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T01:55:16.000Z","msg":"連續幾晚都夢到佢，有一個夢係佢摸住我個頭問我係咪好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有一個夢係夢到佢搵返我，但醒返係一場空，由好開心跌返落谷底...<br />\n佢做決定多數都唔會後悔，係我妄想太多以為可以係返埋一齊啦...唉..."},{"pid":"13efb1ee785466eae65df8e262af3adff678ca7f","tid":849484,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T02:13:16.000Z","msg":"琴晚夢到同佢kiss緊 一醒返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14599156a1b135ab4611dd3646042ed285077a04","tid":849484,"uid":160378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T02:42:08.000Z","msg":"曾經有排會 但宜家冇<br />\n想同佢講句: 仆街死啦你 咪撚再入我個夢到"},{"pid":"b6c9887df5395cbaf384821b764d9de212d741dd","tid":849484,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T02:43:12.000Z","msg":"啱啱夢見完 見到個post先醒起<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1814c4811f7a2d265ed5e3c32c768fb552b37b1","tid":849484,"uid":11468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T02:44:31.000Z","msg":"分左兩個幾月，都仲有夢見佢。每次一醒個人會好炆同sad<br />\n驚會好似樓主咁...半年都仲係咁"},{"pid":"b7bca5a90ddd9df11b80f324a31b6ad80d7dd110","tid":849484,"uid":17531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T02:51:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}